In terms of segmentation, the market is divided based on type, deployment, and end-user. The types of media monitoring tools encompass social media monitoring, print media monitoring, broadcast media monitoring, and online media monitoring, each catering to distinct monitoring requirements. These tools can be deployed either through cloud-based solutions or on-premises setups, providing flexibility and scalability to users. The end-user segments include BFSI, healthcare, retail, media & entertainment, and others, reflecting the diverse industry verticals that leverage media monitoring tools for business insights.

